# Rootstack .gitignore
# By default, personal content is excluded from version control.
# Uncomment sections you want to push (e.g. if you back up privately).

# ── Personal content ──────────────────────────────────────────
About \[You\]/background.md
About \[You\]/values.md
About \[You\]/personality.md
About \[You\]/operating-manual.md
About \[You\]/skills.md
About \[You\]/now.md
About \[You\]/goals/
About \[You\]/stories/
About \[You\]/patterns/
About \[You\]/people/
About \[You\]/learning/

# ── Journal ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
Journal/

# ── Knowledge Base ────────────────────────────────────────────
Knowledge Base/Notes/
Knowledge Base/databases/

# ── Projects ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
Projects/

# ── Content ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
Content/Schedule/

# ── Obsidian ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Keep: community-plugins.json, plugin data.json (pre-configures Journals plugin)
# Exclude: workspace.json (user-specific UI state), plugin binaries (user installs these)
.obsidian/workspace.json
.obsidian/plugins/journals/main.js
.obsidian/plugins/journals/styles.css

# ── System files ──────────────────────────────────────────────
desktop.ini
.DS_Store
*.tmp

# ── What IS pushed by default ─────────────────────────────────
# README.md, CLAUDE.md, AGENTS.md, tools.md (with personal info removed)
# Folder structure and template files
# Skills/ (maintenance automation)
# Content/Style/, Content/Pillars/ (non-personal strategy docs)
# Prompts/ (reusable prompts)
